<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2584472>
    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Zeuxo seurati preparatory female (P.102358). A, habitus (pigmentation similar to male, Fig. 27B); B, pleonites 1– 3 lateral setation; C, pleotelson. Preparatory female (P.102360, P.102360.001). D, antennule; E, antenna; F, uropod. Scale bars: habitus 1 mm, others 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2584472/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2584474>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. Zeuxo seurati preparatory female (P.102360, P.102360.001). A, labrum; B–C left and right mandibles respectively; D, labium; E, maxillule endite; F, maxillule palp; G, maxilliped (one palp omitted for clarity); H, maxilliped palp articles 3–4; I, maxilliped palp article-3 inner (oral) setae; J, epignath. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2584474/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2584476>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25. Zeuxo seurati preparatory female (P.102360, P.102360.001). A, cheliped; B, left chela. Preparatory male (1.96 mm body length). C, antennule (setae omitted); D, cheliped; E, uropod (setae omitted). Preparatory male (2.28 mm body length). F, antennule (setae omitted); G, uropod (setae omitted). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2584476/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2584478>
    dc:description "FIGURE 26. Zeuxo seurati preparatory female (P.102360, P.102360.001). A, pereopod-1; B, pereopod-1 coxa; C, pereopod-2; D, pereopod-2 carpus obscured (mesial) crotchets; E, pereopod-2 claw; F–I, pereopods 3–6 respectively, with details of obscured carpal crotchets; J, pleopod-1 (all setae plumose, many omitted for clarity). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2584478/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2584480>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. Zeuxo seurati preparatory male (P.102362.001). A, cheliped. Copulatory male (P.102358). B, habitus. Copulatory male (P.102363). C, antennule; D, antennule article-2 ventral setae; E, cheliped; F, left chela (lateral and ventral setae omitted). Scale bars: habitus 1 mm, others 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2584480/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2584482>
    dc:description "FIGURE 28. Zeuxo seurati type locality (red marker) and two SFPE-2014 sites on Mangareva (yellow marker) and Taravai (green marker), latter site with Zeuxo seurati." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2584482/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2584484>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Comparison of body size with number of uropod articles. A, Zeuxo seurati and Z. kermadecensis; data points for Z. kermadecensis slightly displaced on y-axis for clarity; non-integer values indicate specimens with uropods of different segment count. B, Zeuxoides rapaitii and Z. rimuwhero; data points for Z. rimuwhero slightly displaced on y-axis for clarity." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2584484/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

